# Merging Collections

This mini project was made for testing coding in TypeScript with Mocha.

## Installation


```bash
npm install --save-dev
```
then
```bash
npm run build
```
then
```bash
npm run serve
```


## Usage

```
Enter collections (separate by pressing Enter after each collection)
Example: 10, 20, 30, 40
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Enter collection: <your inpur>
Enter collection: <your inpur>
Enter collection: <your inpur>
Any sorting do you need? (Asc/Desc/No): <your inpur>
<ANSWER>
```

## For Testing
```bash
npm test
